{"tid":1557635,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係831受傷者之一","createTime":"2019-09-10T07:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:07:33.000Z","uid":52054,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"29b0acfab2bc11bb2693e7b809f645b8b43ea8dc","tid":1557635,"uid":52054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n我係831受傷者之一，雖然我唔清楚有無死人，但會將所經歷講出黎。<br />\n當日被捕時中左三棍，頭爆左，肩骹傷左同手指腫左。<br />\n好似係站個幾鐘先有救護同消防入黎，當時有問救護員傷左幾多人，佢諗左陣話9個（但當時咁亂未必準確）<br />\n然後唔知過左幾耐就坐黨鐵去荔枝角，我地受傷呢批人係最遲走，上到荔枝角出口時已經無記者，但有市民渣機拍攝（應該會影到有幾多傷者上黎）。之後直去醫院，訓左四十個鐘左右番去保釋，去到狗屋見到白板寫左73個名我係其一，有朋友當日拉左都係白板上。  <br />\n之後問番其他人有大部分因為臭格無位十幾個鐘都係停車場，仲要戴哂gear影相屌佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，綠衫爆頭巴好敬佩你，成頭血但縫針個陣都無出過聲話痛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f33902830b2881126eb5fcbdc8352e7164aa0e","tid":1557635,"uid":161126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"8個 搵鬼信"},{"pid":"6f54892d461f0a7d35ea9e345a9f51e1a99f6881","tid":1557635,"uid":205016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"乜撚野借朋友ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40089fcaabc9c8e365e7b7ce8468a6ce7f26be0f","tid":1557635,"uid":205016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6f54892d461f0a7d35ea9e345a9f51e1a99f6881","tid":1557635,"uid":205016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"乜撚野借朋友ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"借親都有好多帶風向"},{"pid":"12a2e3249721a6fb7fe9aee4b79ba1ed1742a3ca","tid":1557635,"uid":52054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"29b0acfab2bc11bb2693e7b809f645b8b43ea8dc","tid":1557635,"uid":52054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r